                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;As reported in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-7759&quot; title=&quot;DROP TABLE makes C* unreachable&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-7759&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-7759&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, Directories throws NPE when trying to remove compaction leftovers on already dropped table.&lt;/p&gt;

